OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUnilever will let Russia   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Femployees be conscripted   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Unilever has said it will let Russian  
OL,6, employees be conscripted to be sent to 
OL,7, Ukraine if they are called up.         
OL,9,FThe consumer goods giant, which has    
OL,10,Fabout 3,000 employees in Russia, has   
OL,11,Fpolicies that cover the well-being and 
OL,12,Fsafety of its workers.                 
OL,14,FHowever, in a letter to campaign group 
OL,15,FB4Ukraine, it said it would comply with
OL,16,FRussian conscription law.              
OL,18,FUnilever has been under pressure to    
OL,19,Fpull out of Russia, but says the       
OL,20,Fsituation is "not straightforward".    
